Conclusion &amp; Stuff The road to becoming a hacker doesn&rsquo;t exist. There are many roads, many paths. This is just an attempt to help create one for you in the most cost-free way possible.
There are other related career paths in Offensive Security, like Penetration Testing, Red Teamer, Security Engineer, Threat Intelligence Analysts, etc.
It&rsquo;s going to be hard. You&rsquo;re going to study a lot, but it is achievable. Take your time and learn and you will be fine. Do not give up.
Thanks for reading, I hope you&rsquo;ve learnt something here!
